					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">Try to check the <a href="http://shiru.untergrund.net/files/src/cc65_nes_examples.zip" class="postlink">current version</a> of the neslib. I added 'split' function today, and it has a number of other improvements added recently. Take a note that the split functionality is very limited: you have to handle PAL/NTSC difference by yourself, code execution time can't exceed frame time (split will be missed otherwise), you have to setup sprite to get sprite0 hit by yourself, you can't scroll bottom part vertically. Hopefully some of these limitations will be removed in the future.</div>

					<br clear="all" /><br />

